summary: This document appears to be a Verizon phone bill or subscriber record from July 2019, produced in response to a legal request (Docket/File #: 2019R01059). The Verizon Security Assistance Team notes that a diligent search revealed no other responsive materials.

keyFacts: Verizon produced this subscriber/billing record in response to a legal request with Docket/File # 2019R01059, indicating it was part of an investigation.
The service was active from July 6, 2019, to August 13, 2019, and the bill date was July 24, 2019.
The record shows two specific calls: one from DUNE, NJ to New York, NY on July 10, 2019, and another from DUNE, NJ to Anaheim, CA on July 13, 2019.
The Verizon Security Assistance Team noted that a 'reasonably diligent search' revealed no other documents responsive to the legal request.
The record is for a landline service, and the billing name, customer name, and addresses are not filled in or are redacted in this excerpt.
